            By accessing or using Hasiyu's SMART Goals Template website and services, you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service. If you disagree with any part of these terms, you may not use our services.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Use of Service</h2>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 mt-6">Permitted Use</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-700 mb-4">
            You may use our SMART goals template and related content for:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4 text-slate-700">
            <li>Personal goal setting and planning</li>
            <li>Professional development purposes</li>
            <li>Educational and non-commercial use</li>
            <li>Sharing the template with others (with attribution)</li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 mt-6">Prohibited Use</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-700 mb-4">
            You may NOT:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4 text-slate-700">
            <li>Resell, redistribute, or commercialize our templates without permission</li>
            <li>Remove copyright notices or attributions</li>
            <li>Use our content to create competing products</li>
            <li>Attempt to reverse engineer or copy our website code</li>
            <li>Use our service for any illegal or unauthorized purpose</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Intellectual Property</h2>
          <p class="text-slate-700 mb-4">
            The content, templates, blog posts, and design of this website are owned by Hasiyu and protected by copyright laws. Our templates are provided free for use, but the underlying intellectual property remains ours.
          </p>
          <p class="text-slate-700 mb-4">
            The SMART goals you create using our template are yours. We claim no ownership over your personal goal content.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Disclaimer of Warranties</h2>
          <p class="text-slate-700 mb-4">
            Our service is provided "as is" without warranties of any kind. We make no guarantees that:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4 text-slate-700">
            <li>The service will be uninterrupted or error-free</li>
            <li>Using our templates will guarantee goal achievement</li>
            <li>The content is always accurate or up-to-date</li>
            <li>The service will meet your specific requirements</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Limitation of Liability</h2>
          <p class="text-slate-700 mb-4">
            Hasiyu and its operators will not be liable for any damages arising from:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4 text-slate-700">
            <li>Use or inability to use our service</li>
            <li>Reliance on information provided on our website</li>
            <li>Loss of data or goals created using our templates</li>
            <li>Any decisions made based on our content</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-slate-700 mb-4">
            You use our service at your own risk. We recommend backing up any important goal data.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">User Content and Data</h2>
          <p class="text-slate-700 mb-4">
            When you use our templates, your goal data is stored locally in your browser. We do not have access to or control over this data. You are responsible for:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4 text-slate-700">
            <li>Backing up your goal data</li>
            <li>Ensuring accuracy of information you enter</li>
            <li>Understanding that clearing browser data will delete your goals</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Third-Party Links</h2>
          <p class="text-slate-700 mb-4">
            Our website may contain links to third-party sites. We are not responsible for the content, privacy policies, or practices of these external sites. Clicking external links is at your own risk.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Modifications to Service</h2>
          <p class="text-slate-700 mb-4">
            We reserve the right to:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4 text-slate-700">
            <li>Modify or discontinue any part of our service</li>
            <li>Update our templates and content</li>
            <li>Change pricing (if we introduce paid features in the future)</li>
            <li>Refuse service to anyone for any reason</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Professional Advice Disclaimer</h2>
          <p class="text-slate-700 mb-4">
            Our templates and blog content are for informational purposes only. They do not constitute:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4 text-slate-700">
            <li>Professional career advice</li>
            <li>Financial planning guidance</li>
            <li>Medical or health recommendations</li>
            <li>Legal advice</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-slate-700 mb-4">
            Consult qualified professionals for specific advice related to your situation.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Governing Law</h2>
          <p class="text-slate-700 mb-4">
            These Terms of Service are governed by and construed in accordance with applicable laws. Any disputes will be resolved in the appropriate courts.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Changes to Terms</h2>
          <p class="text-slate-700 mb-4">
            We may update these Terms of Service at any time. Significant changes will be posted on this page with an updated "Last updated" date. Continued use of our service after changes constitutes acceptance of the new terms.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Contact Information</h2>
          <p class="text-slate-700 mb-4">
            If you have questions about these Terms of Service, contact us at:
          </p>
          <p class="text-slate-700 mb-4">
            Email: <a href="mailto:hi@hasiyu.com" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">hi@hasiyu.com</a>
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Severability</h2>
          <p class="text-slate-700 mb-4">
            If any provision of these terms is found to be unenforceable, the remaining provisions will continue in full force and effect.
          </p>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
